<p align="justify"><span>“I LOVE U</span><span>，</span><span>25</span><span>号再送，可以吗，拜托。</span><span>”8</span><span>月</span><span>17</span><span>日凌晨</span><span>2</span><span>点</span><span>31</span><span>分，在重庆市经营鲜花店的李先生收到了第一个鲜花</span><span>预订单</span><span>，商品是</span><span>“</span><span>怦然心动</span><span>”</span><span>红玫瑰花束</span><span>。</span></p>
